De_ED_blast

This is in no way a decompile or edit of the original map (included). 
The map remains the same all credit to Junks. 
Only things added are 8 spawn points and an overview.
Name change is simply to avoid confusion, also you may need to keep the original for ED matches as sv_pure may kick this map as not being the original due to spawns and overview being added.

Standard de_ style map with 2 bomb spots
This is Enemy Down's official Counter-Strike Source map. 
It was created by Junks who is a member of the ED admin team. 
This map is available to use in ED matches and will be featured in ED cup and league events.

copy the cstrike file and paste into

C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\**YOUR USER NAME**\counter-strike source

Have Fun,

Obii August 2007
http://irishpirates.org




de_blast_ed

Designed and created by Junks (daniel.scott23@ntlworld.com, #snipers on Quakenet)

This map was made for Enemy Down (http://www.enemydown.co.uk) for use in their ladders and league.

Place the .bsp file in your C:\Program Files\Valve\Steam\SteamApps\YOURUSERNAME\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps folder.

All custom textures have been embedded.

Enjoy,

Junks, August 2005
